规则说明：
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
|    rule id    |                                V517                                |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
|   rule name   |                      RepeatedConditionPattern                      |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| rule category |                              Repeated                              |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
|   rule check  |                          重复的if条件语句                          |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
|    message    | The use of 'if (A) {...} else if (A) {...}' pattern was detected.  |
|               |          There is a probability of logical error presence.         |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

